HRRR-Alaska Data#

This will plot HRRR-Alaska data. There are additional ‚Äúproducts‚Äù available than are shown here.

[1]:

from herbie import Herbie
from toolbox import EasyMap, pc
from paint.standard2 import cm_tmp

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import cartopy.crs as ccrs

[2]:

H = Herbie(
    "2021-07-19",
    model="hrrrak",
    product="sfc",
    fxx=6,
)

‚úÖ Found ‚îä model=hrrrak ‚îä product=sfc ‚îä 2021-Jul-19 00:00 UTC F06 ‚îä GRIB2 @ aws ‚îä IDX @ aws

    ax = EasyMap("50m", crs=ds.herbie.crs, figsize=[10, 8]).STATES().ax

p = ax.pcolormesh(
    ds.longitude,
    ds.latitude,
    ds.t2m,
    transform=pc,
    **cm_tmp(units="K").cmap_kwargs,
)
plt.colorbar(
    p,
    ax=ax,
    orientation="horizontal",
    pad=0.05,
    **cm_tmp(units="K").cbar_kwargs,
)

ax.set_title(ds.t2m.GRIB_name, loc="right")
ax.set_title(f"{ds.model.upper()}: {H.product_description}", loc="left")
